 	<div id="main-article-info">

		
		
			<h1 itemprop="name headline  "
								>Caroline Charles: 50 years of British fashion – in pictures</h1>
		
					<p itemprop="description" id="stand-first"
				 class="stand-first-alone"                data-component="comp : r2 : Gallery : standfirst_cta"
			>From the miniskirts and bob cuts of the 60s to the floral prints and shoulder pads of the 80s, Caroline Charles has been a constant force in British fashion for more than 50 years. A new book celebrates her life's work with behind-the-scenes images, scrapbook pictures and long forgotten collections. Here are some of the best</p>
		
		
  	</div>

